{"tid":363141,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"原創曲：寂寞香煙","createTime":"2017-08-17T12:17:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T10:56:59.000Z","uid":117184,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d13d59884569b0992c25eb5a896ce9d6b1d0e502","tid":363141,"uid":117184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:17:41.000Z","msg":"各位巴打支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歌詞本身係一首由朋友寫的詩，小弟見幾得意將佢作成一首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_RQcF0EfqQk&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_RQcF0EfqQk%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=963wBI5SM1HAvGOLyy79mf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=f6d992a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_RQcF0EfqQk&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n寂寞香煙<br />\n作詞:JN<br />\n太悶太熱 無法入眠 <br />\n很想吸一口煙<br />\n煙火點起 燃亮從前 <br />\n燃亮那首詩<br />\n寂寞~香煙<br />\n爺在抽著<br />\n寂寞~香煙<br />\n心在思念<br />\n寂寞~香煙<br />\n伴我過夜<br />\n寂寞~香煙<br />\n盼妳在這<br />\n寂寞~香煙<br />\n沉睡於這仲夏<br />\n寂寞~香煙<br />\n飄得累嗎<br />\n寂寞~香煙<br />\n終會消散<br />\n寂寞~香煙<br />\n觸得到你吧"},{"pid":"5f6ac436d5037548e5081e55ff771137240535bf","tid":363141,"uid":45173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb23a21bd17727fa5e424515e43a48d376bf006","tid":363141,"uid":117184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:43:01.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d579c9e517ad25a0a9915b60022f758f51c72924","tid":363141,"uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2b10197a23c106a2f7d5a5e1cda0cce12e3800","tid":363141,"uid":117184,"like":0,"dislike"